Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這海報…是那個時候的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得真晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火還是沒能放成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  必須要道歉的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都想道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向乃乃香  向小春
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實  全都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  對不起  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果  只能放我帶來的線香花火了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.94,0:21:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶來的放了七年都吸足了水分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.86,0:21:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是戶川同學也在就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}線香花火真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.28,0:21:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:21:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常地  非常地…
